{"tid":1682973,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：女副官暈低 娥特掂行掂過 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-10-30T11:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T13:54:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c3aed96351b6924b6834a90f6d31f196ff0f15","tid":1682973,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191030/20796663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796663&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt32LZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=dce04b71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796663&h=54e56bfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20191030/20796663</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：女副官暈低 娥特掂行掂過 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191030/large/1572368151_4f0d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191030%2Flarge%2F1572368151_4f0d.gif&h=b7b4ad77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭副官、女G4陳嘉怡記者會暈倒，要由其他人攙扶。馬泉崇攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八方記得有個政圈中人講過，有時要睇商界人士有冇良心，靠佢自己講冇用，睇佢點對下屬就知。特首林鄭月娥噚日朝早如常喺行會前見傳媒，因之前《金融時報》傳出中央有意換走佢，所以好多中外傳媒到場採訪。<br />\n<br />\n話說777回應記者提問到尾段，在場駐守嘅林鄭副官、女G4陳嘉怡突然暈倒，在場發出「嘭」一聲嘅巨響，記者好多都嚇一跳，現場所見陳嘉怡嘴唇蒼白，要由其他人攙扶下離開。不過作為佢老闆嘅777，當時只係向陳嘉怡方向一望，之後繼續回應記者提問。當記者會完，好多記者走去睇吓陳嘉怡點，但777連問都冇問，轉身離開現場，完全冇任何表示。<br />\n<br />\n特首辦回覆話，副官感到不適，佢當時清醒，自行上救護車送院治理。作為老闆嘅777，見到下屬喺佢側邊暈倒，可以咁不聞不問直行直過，佢對一般小市民會點？怕且不難想像。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：母校搣柴網民追殺 何執葉鯁花生陣亡 (李八方)"},{"pid":"a6d0ce013942c56224f8cc5cf993ffcb6146c399","tid":1682973,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:34:58.000Z","msg":"11.2 維園見<br />\n勿忘721 805 811 831 101"},{"pid":"e63481e4289f747a55c3c24664438d22ee2e7a89","tid":1682973,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:35:48.000Z","msg":"that police officier has no stake in the society"},{"pid":"43724122736f2334ea6fbc828ce3e2ca8f3b24ec","tid":1682973,"uid":259600,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9MvXncX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9MvXncX.jpg&h=8f96875d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b9d8b9168a1e8e06bfc492de4c7c20d318ccc47","tid":1682973,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:54:23.000Z","msg":"已經有13個英美參議員/單位就GPhone出聲<br />\n快啲Rt and like and reply哂佢<br />\n全部響哂<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> /Task1</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt32LZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=38f7cfbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"}]}